{"title":"Pablo Mas","markdown":{"yaml":{"title":"Pablo Mas","image":"profile.png","resources":"cv.pdf","about":{"template":"jolla","image-shape":"round","image-width":"12em","links":[{"text":"Email","icon":"envelope","href":"mailto:pablovn.mas@gmail.com"},{"text":"GitHub","icon":"github","href":"https://github.com/pablo-mas"},{"text":"LinkedIn","icon":"linkedin","href":"https://www.linkedin.com/in/pablo-mas/"},{"text":"Twitter","icon":"twitter","href":"https://twitter.com/pablomasvn"},{"text":"CV","icon":"file-text","href":"cv.pdf"}],"id":"ppc"}},"containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n\n<div style=\"text-align: justify\"> \n\n\n🧪 I am a PhD candidate at **ENS Ulm** (supervised by Pr. Rodolphe Vuilleumier) and a research scientist at **Sanofi** (Integrated Drug Design team), working on machine learning applied to drug discovery and theoretical chemistry. \n\n🧠 I previously interned at **INRIA** and **ICM** in the **Aramis Lab**, working on Graph Neural Network for image segmentation and graph topological feature extraction to classify Alzheimer's disease patients. \n\n🧑‍🏫 I teach data science at **Le Wagon** coding bootcamp and supervise final student projects.\n\n⛷️ I am a huge ski fan and casual handball player.\n\n📧 Feel free to contact me to have a chat or a coffee ! \n\n</div>\n\n\n\n<br>\n**🏗️ This website is still under construction 🏗️**\n\n\n"},"formats":{"html":{"execute":{"fig-width":7,"fig-height":5,"fig-format":"retina","fig-dpi":96,"df-print":"default","error":false,"eval":true,"cache":null,"freeze":false,"echo":true,"output":true,"warning":true,"include":true,"keep-md":false,"keep-ipynb":false,"ipynb":null,"enabled":null,"daemon":null,"daemon-restart":false,"debug":false,"ipynb-filters":[],"engine":"markdown"},"render":{"keep-tex":false,"keep-source":false,"keep-hidden":false,"prefer-html":false,"output-divs":true,"output-ext":"html","fig-align":"default","fig-pos":null,"fig-env":null,"code-fold":"none","code-overflow":"scroll","code-link":false,"code-line